Dependencies
============

Core:

* mono-mcs      - http://www.mono-project.com
* libglib2.0-cil
* libgtk2.0-cil
* libglade2.0-cil


Instalation
===========

Right now the Makefile is not functional yet, so run the following command from the console to compile the source code:

mcs -out:BillReminder.exe *.cs -pkg:glade-sharp-2.0 -pkg:gtk-sharp-2.0

Now, run BillReminder from the command line with the following command:

mono BillReminder.exe

